RuleListPageHelper<R extends Rule>
public static final class RuleListPageHelper.RuleQueryResults<R extends Rule> extends com.guidewire.pl.system.database.impl.WrappingQueryProcessor<R> implements IQueryBeanResult<R>
Defines a IQueryBeanResult on the RuleListPageHelper.RuleQueryResults subtype that wraps the base result for a query on RuleListPageHelper.RuleQueryResults and caches the associated RuleVersion and Status. The query should include the associated RuleVersion in its join.
